data.description: Your Dream Home Awaits! Discover Angleton's Finest Three-Bedroom Gem! Nestled in the heart of Angleton, this three-bedroom, two-bathroom charmer invites you to experience a harmonious blend of comfort and convenience. Step into the generous living room that flows into the expansive kitchen, creating an entertainer's delight. Abundant cabinet space and a delightful dining area enhance the home's allure. With vinyl flooring throughout and recently renovated bathrooms, this turnkey home exudes a sense of elegance. The enchantment continues outdoors, where a generously sized, fully fenced backyard beckons you to bask in tranquility. A detached two-car garage and additional driveway space complete this peaceful haven. Make this Angleton gem your own today!
